title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 15 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 15 2022
description:
Colorado GOP Senate candidate Joe O'Dea joins Clay and Buck on day nervous Biden travels to Colorado to prop up failing incumbent Michael Bennet. MSNBC's Kornacki says GOP has 30-point advantage on economy, Biden traveling to blue states Colorado, Oregon. New poll shows Ron Johnson up 6 points in Wisconsin. Ohio Senate Candidate JD Vance joins C&B fresh off his debate knockout of Tim Ryan. Recap of latest polling data to end the show.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
